categories: Category:Military officers of the Sith Empire

nodes.text: Tebar was a male Human sergeant of the Sith Empire living during the Galactic War. In 3642 BBY he was stationed on the Harrower-class dreadnought White Nova when it boarded the Galactic Republic Thranta-class corvette Dorin's Sky.
Sergeant Tebar appears in Star Wars: The Old Republic as an NPC on the White Nova, who begins the flashpoint "Boarding Party".
